<cb:div type="nanchuan-notes">
<head>漢譯南傳大藏經 註解</head>
<p>
<note n="0243001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0243001">以上一偈半出自 Sutta-nipāta 637。同處稱之為婆羅門，故取為對格。</note>
<note n="0243002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0243002">Samantacakkhu（徧眼）。</note>
<note n="0244001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0244001">讀為 anekatāla papatiṁ（暹羅本）。</note>
<note n="0244002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0244002">tāla 即 vitasti（搩），為長度之單位，vitasti = 12 anguli，為張開拇指與中指間之長度。</note>
<note n="0244003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0244003">Samphusita（觸）。</note>
<note n="0245001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0245001">讀為 pannarase yadā candaṁ（暹羅本）。</note>
<note n="0245002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0245002">依暹羅本訂正為 niyyante。</note>
<note n="0245003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0245003">Sudhaja（善幡）。</note>
<note n="0246001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0246001">kakkāru 天華之一。</note>
<note n="0246002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0246002">Sattuttama（最勝有情）。</note>
<note n="0247001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0247001">mandārava 譯為天妙華。</note>
<note n="0247002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0247002">Jutindhara（輝持）。</note>
<note n="0248001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0248001">Kukkuṭa（雞）。</note>
<note n="0248002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0248002">讀為 vasanti te（暹羅本）。</note>
<note n="0248003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0248003">Phullanāyaka（花嚮導）。異本為 Pupphanāmakā（叫做花者）。</note>
<note n="0249001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0249001">Bhūtagaṇa（鬼群）。</note>
<note n="0249002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0249002">tiṇasūla 素馨之一種。</note>
<note n="0249001-1" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0249001-1">Suvaccha（善積）。</note>
<note n="0250002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0250002">讀為 dīpo pajjalate tathā（暹羅本）。</note>
<note n="0250003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0250003">讀為 hāsaṁ mama（暹羅本訂正為 mamaṁ）viditvāna（暹羅本）。</note>
<note n="0250004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0250004">從異本之 okiriṁ ahaṁ（暹羅本亦同）。</note>
<note n="0250005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0250005">Mahāratha（大車）。</note>
<note n="0251001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0251001">Tamonuda（驅闇）。</note>
<note n="0252001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0252001">kakudha 鷄冠之意，又作樹名。暹羅本為 kukkuṭa（鷄）。</note>
<note n="0252002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0252002">讀為 vattasampanno（暹羅本）。</note>
<note n="0252003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0252003">訂為 Puññāpuññesu kovido（依暹羅本）。</note>
<note n="0252004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0252004">從暹羅本讀為 bhitvā。</note>
<note n="0252005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0252005">訂正為 tañ ca dānam daditvā' haṁ（依暹羅本）。</note>
</p>
</cb:div>
